name: David M. Strickland
tagline: Software Engineer. Android geek. Coding enthusiast. Technology fanatic. Lifelong learner.
body:
### About
I'm a Software Engineer at [Numbers Place Inc.](http://www.numbersplace.com) during normal business hours. I spend nights and weekends learning about new technologies, frameworks, and gadgets. I've also been known to contribute to Open Source projects when I have free time.

### Current Interests
I'm currently interested in [civic hacking](https://opengovdata.io/2014/civic-hacking/) and [open data](https://blog.okfn.org/2013/10/03/defining-open-data/)

### Contact
I'm always interested in exploring new projects.
